snippet.title: All-Star Fruit Racing: Early Access OUT NOW on Steam!
snippet.description:
Buy Now on Steam (in Early Access): http://store.steampowered.com/app/673190/AllStar_Fruit_Racing/ 

All-Star Fruit Racing is the kart racing game you’ve been waiting for! Easy to learn but hard to master, choose your character, customize your kart and play the way that tempts you most!
